elements.title: the Majestic

elements.title: 1995 Burlington mayoral election
elements.contents: ... that Peter Clavelle's victory in the 1995 Burlington mayoral election made him its first mayor to return to office after losing it since James Edmund Burke in 1933?

elements.title: Napir-Asu

elements.title: Bally's Chicago
